<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 12:31:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>渣打银行任命前摩根大通高管马莱拉领导支付业务</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/stanchart-appoints-former-jpmorgan-exec-mallela-to-lead-payments</link><description>渣打银行已任命摩根大通区块链部门前全球联席主管领导其全球支付业务，并继续对其现金管理系统进行现代化改造。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/im6YV5s8adrs/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/stanchart-appoints-former-jpmorgan-exec-mallela-to-lead-payments</guid></item><item><title>特朗普就加密议程与银行的对抗升级</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/trump-escalates-confrontation-with-banks-over-crypto-agenda</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普总统警告银行不要削弱他的加密货币议程，并推动通过一项名为《清晰法案》的市场结构法案，从而加剧了与金融业在重塑美国数字资产监管方式的立法问题上的对抗。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/irTCQOplopOg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 23:19:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/trump-escalates-confrontation-with-banks-over-crypto-agenda</guid></item><item><title>由于长期战争的风险给加密货币带来压力，比特币回落</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/bitcoin-btc-slide-starts-anew-as-iran-uncertainty-drags-on</link><description>由于人们越来越担心伊朗战争将继续升级，风险资产的更广泛抛售加剧，比特币徘徊在 68,000 美元左右，抹去了周一的涨幅。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioDoooC3HqMo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 08:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/bitcoin-btc-slide-starts-anew-as-iran-uncertainty-drags-on</guid></item><item><title>塞勒强调向企业推销时的安全性</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-03/strategy-s-saylor-puts-emphasis-on-safety-in-latest-sales-pitch-to-corporations</link><description>永久安全策略&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDHgeMoK8x_0/v6/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 22:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-03/strategy-s-saylor-puts-emphasis-on-safety-in-latest-sales-pitch-to-corporations</guid></item><item><title>CFTC 主席表示，美国加密货币永续期货即将推出</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/us-crypto-linked-perpetual-futures-coming-soon-cftc-chair-says</link><description>美国最高衍生品监管机构计划在几周内允许加密货币的永续期货合约，将迄今为止几乎完全存在于离岸交易所的交易工具引入境内。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iOgtymQCiZNE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 19:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/us-crypto-linked-perpetual-futures-coming-soon-cftc-chair-says</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行文件警告称，稳定币可能对货币政策构成重大风险</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/stablecoins-could-pose-major-risks-to-monetary-policy-ecb-paper</link><description>欧洲央行的一份工作文件警告称，稳定币的广泛采用将对欧元区银行和欧洲央行的货币主权构成重大风险，特别是与美元等外币挂钩时。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyn1khea7JJk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/stablecoins-could-pose-major-risks-to-monetary-policy-ecb-paper</guid></item><item><title>红杉资本和创始人为 Latam 的 ARQ 筹集 7000 万美元资金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/sequoia-founders-fund-back-70-million-raise-for-latam-s-arq</link><description>ARQ 表示，风险投资公司红杉资本和 Founders Fund 正在通过融资 7000 万美元投资拉丁美洲金融应用程序 ARQ。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iiNyS2Imx3rw/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/sequoia-founders-fund-back-70-million-raise-for-latam-s-arq</guid></item><item><title>加密货币的 24 小时承诺受到地缘政治现实检验</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-s-24-hour-promise-gets-a-geopolitical-reality-check</link><description>长期以来，比特币一直被宣传为提供其他市场无法提供的东西：24 小时实时了解全球风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4AG3wmEmoho/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 17:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-s-24-hour-promise-gets-a-geopolitical-reality-check</guid></item><item><title>随着市场波动加剧，比特币涨至 70,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/bitcoin-advances-toward-70-000-as-volatility-increases</link><description>随着中东战争不断升级，全球金融市场波动性加剧，比特币推向近期交易区间的上限。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifHg170SjOsQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 16:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/bitcoin-advances-toward-70-000-as-volatility-increases</guid></item><item><title>银行监管机构采取行动限制美国稳定币奖励</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/federal-bank-regulator-moves-to-restrict-us-stablecoin-rewards</link><description>美国货币监理署提出规则，限制公司通过白标平台推出品牌稳定币并提供与之相关的奖励，这是该机构为实施唐纳德·特朗普总统于 7 月签署的联邦加密货币法的首次重大尝试。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iF__U9SRvdHk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 22:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/federal-bank-regulator-moves-to-restrict-us-stablecoin-rewards</guid></item><item><title>稳定币发行人 Tether 使用德勤提供 USAT 储备报告</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/stablecoin-issuer-tether-uses-deloitte-for-usat-reserve-report</link><description>多年来，Tether Holdings SA 一直表示主要会计师事务所不愿提供审计服务，但现在，Tether Holdings SA 收到了德勤对其 USAT 稳定币有史以来第一份准备金报告的认可​​，该报告是为了遵守美国新法规而推出的。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igbJWXXDFJAo/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 20:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/stablecoin-issuer-tether-uses-deloitte-for-usat-reserve-report</guid></item><item><title>Saylor 的策略通过使用普通股加大比特币购买力度</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/saylor-s-strategy-mstr-steps-up-bitcoin-btc-buys-by-using-common-shares</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 购买了价值超过 2 亿美元的比特币，并转向普通股为其大部分收购提供资金，尽管承诺将依靠其永久优先股。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ie1Zx_V76eOQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 15:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/saylor-s-strategy-mstr-steps-up-bitcoin-btc-buys-by-using-common-shares</guid></item></channel></rss>